<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.9.3">
<l>uruppiṇi naṅkaiyait tērēṟṟik koṇṭu</l>
<l>viruppuṟṟaṅ kēkavi raintetir vantu</l>
<l>cerukkuṟṟāṉ vīrañ citaiya talaiyaic</l>
<l>ciraittiṭṭāṉ vaṉmaiyaip pāṭippaṟa</l>
<l rend="indent">tēvaki ciṅkattaip pāṭippaṟa.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Jump and sing about the strength of him who,</l>
<l rend="indent">with desire rising, lifted and carried away</l>
<l rend="indent">the lady Rukmiṇī in [his] chariot,</l>
<l>[and] shaved the head of the prideful one,</l>
<l rend="indent">having swiftly come there in opposition,</l>
<l>so that [his] bravery was broken.</l>
<l>Jump and sing about the lion of Devakī!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
